OL,3,CMore than one pub a day set to close
OL,4,Cthis year, industry body warns
OL,6,FThe equivalent of more than one pub a
OL,7,Fday is set to close this year across
OL,8,FGreat Britain, an industry body has
OL,9,Fwarned.
OL,11,FThe British Beer and Pub Association
OL,12,F(BBPA) has estimated that 378 pubs
OL,13,Fwill close this year across England,
OL,14,FWales and Scotland, which it said
OL,15,Fwould amount to more than 5,600 direct
OL,16,Fjob losses.
OL,18,FThe BBPA has urged the Government to
OL,19,Freform business rates for the sector.
