OL,6,FThe trade association said reducing
OL,7,Fthe cumulative tax and regulatory
OL,8,Fburden would help more pubs stay open,
OL,9,Fleading to more investment and jobs
OL,10,Fwhile also protecting spaces that, for
OL,11,Fmany communities, "are the only places
OL,12,Fleft to gather".
OL,14,FBBPA chief executive Emma McClarkin
OL,15,Fsaid: "Pubs are trading well but most
OL,16,Fof the money that goes into the till
OL,17,Fgoes straight back out in bills and
OL,18,Ftaxes.
